# CLIP ChangeLog for media-video/vlc

*vlc-2.2.4-r3 (19 Jul 2017)

  19 Jul 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.2.4-r3.ebuild, -vlc-2.2.4-r2.ebuild:
  Add more clip-deps flags

*vlc-2.2.4-r2 (05 Apr 2017)

  05 Apr 2017; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.2.4-r2.ebuild, -vlc-2.2.1-r1.ebuild:
  update for chromium 57.0.2987.98

*vlc-2.2.1-r1 (23 Feb 2016)
