*vlc-2.1.4-r1 (02 Jul 2014)

  27 Aug 2014; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +files/vlc-revert-win32-yadif-changes.patch:
  Revert WIN32 specific changes in yadif (deinterlacer) asm code, which don't
  build on CLIP i386

  02 Jul 2014; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.1.4-r1.ebuild, -vlc-2.1.4.ebuild:
  Force rebuild, newer ffmpeg.

