*vlc-2.1.0 (08 Nov 2013)

  08 Nov 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.1.0.ebuild, -vlc-2.0.7-r1.ebuild,
  +files/vlc-2.1.0-TomWij-bisected-PA-broken-underflow.patch,
  +files/vlc-2.1.0-avcodec-check-update-buffered_time-earlier-so-we-sho.patch,
  +files/vlc-2.1.0-libva-1.2.1-compat.patch,
  +files/vlc-2.1.0-newer-rdp.patch,
  +files/vlc-2.1.0-transcode-don-t-check-drift-if-we-have-VLC_TS_INVALI.patch:
  Bump to latest. Add dependency on automake-1.14, since autopoint fails
  with earlier versions.

