  Bump to final 2.0.6 release.

*vlc-2.0.5_p20130405 (05 Apr 2013)

  05 Apr 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.0.5_p20130405.ebuild, -vlc-2.0.5.ebuild,
  +files/vlc-2.0.5-xcb-more-depth.patch:
  Bump to a recent snapshot.
  Add a patch to test more display depths in xcb video backend,
  needed to find a valid depth in tigervnc.

*vlc-2.0.5 (28 Dec 2012)

  28 Dec 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.0.5.ebuild, -vlc-2.0.4.ebuild:
  Bump to latest to rebuild with pulseaudio support.
  Add veriexec entry for network access.

*vlc-2.0.4 (13 Nov 2012)

  13 Nov 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.0.4.ebuild, -vlc-2.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Security update to latest.

*vlc-2.0.3-r1 (08 Oct 2012)

  12 Oct 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  vlc-2.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Remove multiple dependencies on zlib.

  09 Oct 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  vlc-2.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Add DESCRIPTION_FR and CATEGORY_FR. clip-deps fixes.

  08 Oct 2012; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +vlc-2.0.3-r1.ebuild, -vlc-2.0.3.ebuild:
  Don't enable macosx USE flags by default. 
  Use CPREFIX in docdir.
  Drop dependency on truetype fonts (no need for subtitles for now).
